**Rules:**

- Describe WHAT the next code block does
- Present tense verbs: "Get", "Parse", "Check", "Set", "Add", "Create"
- **Omit articles** ("the", "a", "an"): "Get input value" not "Get the input value"
- No period at end
- Blank line before comment, no blank line after

